13) List images
docker images
or
docker image ls
14) Download image
docker pull image-name
15) Upload image
docker push image-name
16) Search image
docker search image-name
17) Delete image
docker rmi image-name
18) Create image from container
docker commit container-id image-name
19) Create image from Dockerfile
docker build -t image-name .
Working with Docker Containers
20) List running containers
docker container ls
21) List all containers
docker ps -a
22) Start container
docker start container-id
23) Stop container
docker stop container-id
24) Restart container
docker restart container-id
25) Restart with delay
docker restart -t 10 container-id
26) Remove stopped container
docker rm container-id
27) Remove running container
docker rm -f container-id
28) Stop all containers
docker stop $(docker ps -aq)
29) Remove all containers
docker rm $(docker ps -aq)
30) View logs
docker logs container-id
31) Check ports
docker port container-id
32) Inspect container
docker inspect container-id
33) Run container
docker run image-name
Docker Networking
34) List networks
docker network ls
35) Inspect network
docker network inspect network-name
36) Create network
docker network create network-name
37) Delete network
docker network rm network-name
